  <entry>
    <title>快速入门</title>
    <link href="/2023/05/02/hello-world/"/>
    <url>/2023/05/02/hello-world/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我就不删这个了吧</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>第一篇文章</title>
    <link href="/2023/03/30/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/"/>
    <url>/2023/03/30/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是我写的第一篇文章，完全不知道该做什么，也不晓得什么排版</p><h2 id="这是一味的复制"><a href="#这是一味的复制" class="headerlink" title="这是一味的复制"></a>这是一味的复制</h2><p>完全不知道该干嘛呢~</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">或许这个东西是这样的？<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="尝试着纪录自己的代码"><a href="#尝试着纪录自己的代码" class="headerlink" title="尝试着纪录自己的代码"></a>尝试着纪录自己的代码</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br>int <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">main</span></span>()<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">return</span> 0;<br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不知道会不会出错呢？</p><h2 id="或许可以加点本地图片？"><a href="#或许可以加点本地图片？" class="headerlink" title="或许可以加点本地图片？"></a>或许可以加点本地图片？</h2><p>来试试吧<div align=left><img src="/img/bmlogo4.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  
